<title>UK: Lonrho shares up after Kleinwort upgrade.</title>
<headline>Lonrho shares up after Kleinwort upgrade.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-01-17</dateline>
<text>
<p>Shares in conglomerate Lonrho Plc edged higher on Friday after analysts at Dresdner Kleinwort Benson upgraded their recommendation on the stock to &quot;hold&quot; from &quot;sell&quot;, dealers said.</p>
<p>By 1245 GMT, Lonrho shares were 1/2p firmer at 127-1/2.</p>
<p>Analysts at Dresdner Kleinwort Benson were not immediately available to comment.</p>
<p>-- Andrew Marshall, London newsroom +44 171 542 4367</p>
